  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether fostamatinib is safe and effective in
      treating patients with persistent/chronic Immune Thrombocytopenic Purpura (ITP) over a 2 year
      period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
